The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Good Morning
      Hello It's Sunday , April 27 , 2008                
	School festival    Take part in Creation 2008, an inter-school festival in association with t2, on the Victoria Memorial premises, 8am to noon.        
	Creative writing    Take your kids to a creative writing workshop for children between 9 and 16 at Oxford Bookstore Junior, 4pm to 6pm.         
	education Fair    Check out Kolkata Education Fair at Netaji Indoor Stadium, 11am to 7.30pm.        
	Earth Day    Attend World Earth Day events at Starmark, Lord Sinha Road, 5pm.         
	Furniture bazaar    Drop in at Furniture Bazaar 2008 at Ice Skating Rink, 11am to 8pm.        
	Eye on art    Visit Canvas, Paper and Bronze, a painting and sculpture exhibition , at Academy of Fine Arts, 3pm to 8pm.                                                                                                                                                              
